name: Demonissi Gori
desc: This marks the consecutive year that Honda has been honored with the Best Value Brand award by Kelley Blue Book’s KBB.com. Editors noted how consistent “reliability, resale value, and quality” contributed to the win. When you are driving at night above 25 mph (40 km/h) and the headlight lever is in the low-beam position with the switch rotated to AUTO, the system intuitively changes between low and high beams depending on surrounding conditions.
